== 發行 ==
=== 评价 ===
影片获得影评人褒贬不一的评价。[[烂番茄|烂番茄]]基于148条评论，给予影片43%的“新鲜度”，平均得分5.4/10分。网站共识指出：“《废柴特工》有点有意思的点子，但和它那死板的主角一样，影片太容易偏题，没能发掘出真正的潜力<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american_ultra/|title=American Ultra|website=Rotten Tomatoes|accessdate=2016-01-17|archive-date=2022-05-02|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220502233535/https://www.rottentomatoes.com/m/american_ultra}}</ref>。”[[Metacritic|Metacritic]]根据31条评论打出50/100分，表示“好坏参半”<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.metacritic.com/movie/american-ultra|title=American Ultra reviews|website=Metacritic|accessdate=2015-09-09|archive-date=2022-06-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220621190319/https://www.metacritic.com/movie/american-ultra}}</ref>。[[影院评分|影院评分]]表示从A+级到F级，影片观众平均得分“B-”<ref>{{cite web |url=http://deadline.com/2015/08/straight-outta-compton-sinister-2-american-ultra-agent-47-box-office-opening-1201503182/ |title=‘Compton’ To Cross $100M Today As August Marketplace Chills Out – Late Night B.O. Update |work=Deadline.com |accessdate=2015-08-22 |archive-date=2022-04-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220418043557/https://deadline.com/2015/08/straight-outta-compton-sinister-2-american-ultra-agent-47-box-office-opening-1201503182/ }}</ref>。

《[[卫报|卫报]]》的{{le|马克·科莫德|Mark Kermode}}给予影片2星评价（满分5星）：“杰西·艾森伯格和克里斯汀·斯图尔特勇敢献出一道暴力多多，笑点少得可怜的无政府主义大杂烩<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/sep/06/american-ultra-review-kristen-stewart | title=American Ultra review – stoner turns state killer to little comic effect | work=Mark Kermode | publisher=The Guardian | date=2015-09-06 | accessdate=2015-09-08 | archive-date=2022-06-23 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220623170713/https://www.theguardian.com/film/2015/sep/06/american-ultra-review-kristen-stewart }}</ref>。”《{{le|麦卡莱斯特首府新闻报|McAlester News-Capital}}》的大卫·迪氏曼（{{lang|en|David Dishman}}）写道：“《废柴特工》在‘没有比铁石心肠的冷血杀手更恐怖的事情’的口号下自吹自擂，虽然他们或许是对的，但冷血杀手电影毫无亮点可言<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.mcalesternews.com/news/movie-review-american-ultra-is-ultra-average/article_b54fdf8a-4d93-11e5-8c96-638cc4eea57e.html | title=Movie review: American Ultra is ultra-average | work=David Dishman | publisher=McAlester News-Capital | date=2015-08-28 | accessdate=2015-09-08 | archive-date=2021-06-27 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210627180657/https://www.mcalesternews.com/news/movie-review-american-ultra-is-ultra-average/article_b54fdf8a-4d93-11e5-8c96-638cc4eea57e.html }}</ref>。”

《[[滚石_(杂志)|滚石]]》的[[彼得·崔維斯|彼得·崔維斯]]给予影片2星评价（满分4星）：“电影的扭曲魅力很快便让位给血淋淋的飞溅物。艾森伯格和斯图尔特卖力地喷血。电影承载的东西没有那么多<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/american-ultra-20150819 | title='American Ultra' Movie Review | work=Peter Travers | publisher=Rolling Stone | date=2015-08-19 | accessdate=2015-09-08 | archive-date=2017-12-02 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171202003451/http://www.rollingstone.com/movies/reviews/american-ultra-20150819 }}</ref>。”《[[纽约时报|纽约时报]]》的{{le|尼尔·根茨林格|Neil Genzlinger}}给影片的评价中肯：“许多东西老生常谈，艾森伯格先生和斯图尔特女士也不是特别的黔驴技穷。但迈克找到利用家用物品的搞怪路子为自己，沃特·戈金斯和约翰·雷吉扎莫盘活了愚蠢小角色的潜质，剧情有一到二次的漂亮转折，你最好去空调剧场看片<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/21/movies/review-in-american-ultra-jesse-eisenberg-is-a-stoner-and-a-target.html?referrer=google_kp&_r=0 | title=Review: In ‘American Ultra,’ Jesse Eisenberg Is a Stoner and a Target | work=Neil Genzlinger | publisher=New York Times | date=2015-08-20 | accessdate=2015-09-08 | archive-date=2015-08-26 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150826021604/http://www.nytimes.com/2015/08/21/movies/review-in-american-ultra-jesse-eisenberg-is-a-stoner-and-a-target.html?referrer=google_kp&_r=0 }}</ref>。”

兰迪斯在接受{{le|红纸信媒体|Red Letter Media}}采访时谈到了电影的糟糕的评价和票房表现<ref>{{cite web | url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DR-Dry8Qb4A | title=Red Letter Media, 'A conversation with Max Landis' | date=2015-11-24 | access-date=2016-04-16 | archive-date=2022-04-22 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20220422053559/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DR-Dry8Qb4A }}</ref>。

=== 票房 ===
影片票房表现差强人意，北美地区收益1444.0985万美元，海外收益1269.8539万美元，全球总票房2713.9524美元。预算2800万美元<ref name=BOM />。

上映首周末，影片入账550万美元，在票房榜上位列第六，在当周新上映作品中排行第三，位居《[[凶兆2：雙瘋|凶兆2：雙瘋]]》（1050万美元）和《[[代号47|代号47]]》（830万美元）之后<ref>{{cite web | url=http://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/chart/?yr=2015&wknd=34&p=.htm | title=Weekend Box Office Results for August 21-23, 2015 | work=Box Office Mojo | publisher=Box Office Mojo | date=2015-08-24 | accessdate=2015-09-08 | archive-date=2021-04-04 | archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210404184321/https://www.boxofficemojo.com/weekend/2015W34/ | dead-url=no }}</ref>。

